<L>__{interior coffee shop day}
<A>__{the loudness of the rockabilly song slaps sonny and otis in their faces as they walk inside the door. the sexy sight of mallory doing the ubang stomp stops them in their tracks.}
<C>__{sonny}
<D>__{good god almighty. what the hell is that?}
<C>__{otis}
<D>__{that's a bitch outta hell, son.}
