<D>__{no!}
<A>__{mickey fires the .45. the bullet chinks through the coffee pot mabel's holding and explodes, thunking her in the chest. she hits the floor dead. mickey and mallory join hands and walk over to the pinball cowboy who stands in a pool of his own urine.}
